#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.48"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.48:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.48:0.2"
msgid "5. Jarāvagga"
msgstr "5. Old Age"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.48:0.3"
msgid "48. Catutthapubbārāmasutta"
msgstr "48. At the Eastern Monastery (4th)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.48:1.1"
msgid "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ."
msgstr "The same setting."

msgctxt "sn48.48:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Katinaṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā khīṇāsavo "
"bhikkhu aññaṃ byākaroti:"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, how many faculties must a mendicant develop and cultivate so "
"that they can declare enlightenment:"

msgctxt "sn48.48:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāmī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘I understand: “Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, "
"what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of "
"existence”’?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.224"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.48:2.1"
msgid "“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā … pe …"
msgstr "“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. …”"

msgctxt "sn48.48:2.2"
msgid ""
"“pañcannaṃ kho, bhikkhave, indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā khīṇāsavo "
"bhikkhu aññaṃ byākaroti:"
msgstr ""
"“A mendicant must develop and cultivate five faculties so that they can "
"declare enlightenment."

msgctxt "sn48.48:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāmīti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn48.48:2.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ pañcannaṃ?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn48.48:2.5"
msgid ""
"Saddhindriyassa, vīriyindriyassa, satindriyassa, samādhindriyassa, "
"paññindriyassa—"
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.48:2.6"
msgid ""
"imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"khīṇāsavo bhikkhu aññaṃ byākaroti:"
msgstr ""
"These are the five faculties that a mendicant must develop and cultivate so "
"that they can declare enlightenment:"

msgctxt "sn48.48:2.7"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I understand: “Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, "
"what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of "
"existence”’.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.48:2.8"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
